---
title: Creamy Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto Shrimp with Sweet Peppers and Pearl Couscous
description: Tonight, we're serving up the crave-worthy dish you've been dreaming of! A garlicky sun-dried tomato sauce studded with onions and peppers is draped over shrimp and buttery pearl couscous. Each bite will have you going back for more!
